; ── THE LIPS restriction (22-25 m depth) ─────────────────────────────────────
; Passage narrows sharply. SAR NOTE: width ~1.0 m, height ~0.8 m at tightest.
; Limits rescue equipment transport. Body recovery may require dismantling.
L0    L1    5.5   075   -5   1.5   1.8   1.0   0.8
